    <head>Processing Information</head>
<p>At the time of accessioning, materials were rehoused in an acid-free box. Some folders were replaced when they were noticeably damaged, but the majority of the folders in the collection are original to the donor. The original folder order, as well as folder titles has been retained. No arrangement or other physical interventions have taken place.</p>  </processinfo>
